{"id":"cpv","slug":"cpv-calculator","name":"CPV Calculator","category":"finance","icon":"📺","description":"Calculate Cost Per View for video ad campaigns and estimate total campaign cost.","tags":["cpv","cost per view","advertising","video","finance"],"fields":[{"id":"totalCost","label":"Total Campaign Cost ($)","type":"number","defaultValue":500,"constraint":{"min":0,"step":0.01}},{"id":"totalViews","label":"Total Views","type":"number","defaultValue":25000,"constraint":{"min":1,"step":1}},{"id":"cpv","label":"CPV — Cost Per View ($)","type":"computed","precision":6},{"id":"cpm","label":"CPM (Cost per 1000 views)","type":"computed","precision":4},{"id":"viewsFor100","label":"Views for $100 budget","type":"computed","precision":0}],"groups":[{"id":"inputs","label":"Campaign","fields":["totalCost","totalViews"]},{"id":"outputs","label":"Metrics","fields":["cpv","cpm","viewsFor100"]}],"formulas":{"cpv":"totalCost/totalViews","cpm":"totalCost/totalViews*1000","viewsFor100":"100/(totalCost/totalViews)"},"examples":[{"label":"$500 for 25,000 views","inputs":{"totalCost":500,"totalViews":25000}},{"label":"$1,000 for 50,000 views","inputs":{"totalCost":1000,"totalViews":50000}}]}
